{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":21041,"originalJapaneseLine":"「――――――――ッ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"――――――――! ?\""},{"lineNumber":21042,"originalJapaneseLine":"――――持ち上がらない。","translatedEnglishLine":"――――I can't lift it."},{"lineNumber":21043,"originalJapaneseLine":"あんなに軽々と振り回せた剣が、","translatedEnglishLine":"The sword I used to wield so effortlessly,"},{"lineNumber":21044,"originalJapaneseLine":"今は鉄の塊よりも遙かに重い。","translatedEnglishLine":"Now feels far heavier than a lump of iron."},{"lineNumber":21045,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ……あっ、あああぁぁっ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah... ah, aaaaaagh...!\""},{"lineNumber":21046,"originalJapaneseLine":"勇者としての寿命が、尽きている。","translatedEnglishLine":"My lifespan as a hero is running out."},{"lineNumber":21047,"originalJapaneseLine":"それは分かっていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"I knew that."},{"lineNumber":21048,"originalJapaneseLine":"けれど……戦う資格さえ、もうないのか。","translatedEnglishLine":"But... do I no longer even have the right to fight?"},{"lineNumber":21049,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ば、バカ野郎……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-You idiot...!"},{"lineNumber":21050,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いいだろ、ただ振り回すくらい……！","translatedEnglishLine":"Fine, just let me swing it around...!"},{"lineNumber":21051,"originalJapaneseLine":"　はや、早くしないと、あいつが、ッ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hurry, if I don’t, that guy will...!"},{"lineNumber":21052,"originalJapaneseLine":"血でぬるつく指で、","translatedEnglishLine":"With fingers slippery from blood,"},{"lineNumber":21053,"originalJapaneseLine":"必死に柄を握ろうとするが……叶わない。","translatedEnglishLine":"I desperately try to grip the hilt... but fail."},{"lineNumber":21054,"originalJapaneseLine":"仕方なく視線を転じた……その、足下に。","translatedEnglishLine":"Helplessly, I shift my gaze... down to my feet."},{"lineNumber":21055,"originalJapaneseLine":"　","translatedEnglishLine":""},{"lineNumber":21056,"originalJapaneseLine":"　　＜ぼとっ……ごろっ、ごろごろ……＞","translatedEnglishLine":"　　<Plop... roll, roll, roll...>"},{"lineNumber":21057,"originalJapaneseLine":"「――――――…………え、っ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"――――――…………Eh?\""},{"lineNumber":21058,"originalJapaneseLine":"転がってきた、丸い何かと……目があった。","translatedEnglishLine":"I met eyes with something round that rolled towards me."},{"lineNumber":21059,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"..............................\""},{"lineNumber":21060,"originalJapaneseLine":"朝方に別れた、その顔。","translatedEnglishLine":"That face I parted from at dawn."},{"lineNumber":21061,"originalJapaneseLine":"何度も見た……ずっと、見守るはずの、顔だった。","translatedEnglishLine":"A face I’ve seen many times... a face I was supposed to always watch over."},{"lineNumber":21062,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っ……あ、ぁ……ああ、ぅ、ぁぁっ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Ah, ah... ah, uh, aaah..."},
{"lineNumber":21063,"originalJapaneseLine":"　……ニー……ナ……？」","translatedEnglishLine":"...Ni...ina...?\""},{"lineNumber":21064,"originalJapaneseLine":"応えはない。","translatedEnglishLine":"There’s no response."},{"lineNumber":21065,"originalJapaneseLine":"顔を真っ赤にして怒っていた表情も、","translatedEnglishLine":"The expression of anger with a flushed face,"},{"lineNumber":21066,"originalJapaneseLine":"恥ずかしげにはにかんでいた表情も、もう、亡く――","translatedEnglishLine":"The shy, blushing smile as well, are already gone—"},{"lineNumber":21067,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、ぅ、あ……………………","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, uh, ah……………………"},{"lineNumber":21068,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うあああああああああああああああああああッ！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Uaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaahhh!!\""},{"lineNumber":21069,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うっひょ、ゴーーール……あれ。なんかいる。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Woohoo, GOAL... huh. There's something here."},{"lineNumber":21070,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あらよっと」","translatedEnglishLine":"Alrighty then.\""},{"lineNumber":21071,"originalJapaneseLine":"伏したアリオスの背に、無造作な魔物の足が落ちた。","translatedEnglishLine":"A rough monster’s foot landed on the back of the fallen Arios."},{"lineNumber":21072,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っ、が……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gah...!\""},{"lineNumber":21073,"originalJapaneseLine":"心身から動くだけの力が抜け落ち、","translatedEnglishLine":"The strength to move leaves my body and mind,"},{"lineNumber":21074,"originalJapaneseLine":"アリオスは床に叩きつけられた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Arios was slammed down onto the floor."},{"lineNumber":21075,"originalJapaneseLine":"（ど……ぅ、して……どうして、こんな、っ……！）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Wh...why... why is this happening...!)"},{"lineNumber":21076,"originalJapaneseLine":"「男じゃん。殺しとこうぜ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"He's a man, huh? Let's kill him.\""},{"lineNumber":21077,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あー、ほっとくと隊長に怒られちゃうなー。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah—if we leave him, the captain will get mad.\""},{"lineNumber":21078,"originalJapaneseLine":"　よっこらせ、っと」","translatedEnglishLine":"Alright, here we go.\""},{"lineNumber":21079,"originalJapaneseLine":"魔物兵たちの武器が、振り上がる。","translatedEnglishLine":"The weapons of the monster soldiers rose up."},{"lineNumber":21080,"originalJapaneseLine":"だが、アリオスの視界には、それは入らなかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"But Arios’s vision did not catch them."},{"lineNumber":21081,"originalJapaneseLine":"微動だにしないアリオスの頭に、","translatedEnglishLine":"On Arios's completely still head,"},{"lineNumber":21082,"originalJapaneseLine":"幾つもの凶器が振り下ろされ――――","translatedEnglishLine":"Multiple weapons were brought down—"},{"lineNumber":21083,"originalJapaneseLine":"――魔物の首が、前触れもなく刎ね飛んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"—and a monster’s head was suddenly severed without warning."},{"lineNumber":21084,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はいはい、邪魔邪魔、っと」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, alright, moving aside the obstacles.\""},{"lineNumber":21085,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah…………\""},{"lineNumber":21086,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あれ。納屋の中で、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh. What are you rummaging around inside the barn, Arios?\""},{"lineNumber":21087,"originalJapaneseLine":"　何ごそごそやってるんですか、アリオス」","translatedEnglishLine":"What are you skulking around doing, Arios?\""},

{"lineNumber":21088,"originalJapaneseLine":"「コー、ラ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey, you...\""},{"lineNumber":21089,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はーい。ご無沙汰ですアリオス。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey there. Long time no see, Arios."},{"lineNumber":21090,"originalJapaneseLine":"　エスクードソード、返してもらいに来ましたよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I've come to get back the Escudo Sword.\""}]}

